      "writtenOn": "2018-12-04T01:17:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "my preference is always have tabs because it would solve crbug.com/897041\nthe unintended behavior can be seen in https://ci.chromium.org/p/chromium/builders/luci.chromium.ci/Win7%20Tests%20%281%29/85989\n\nthe user wants to see the blamelist, but it is displayed below very tall properties table",
      "parentUuid": "71e2a570_eebacbf2",
